We demonstrate two interactive possibilities enabled by our lens-array-based hardware
prototype, and realtime GPU-accelerated software pipeline. Additionally, we describe
a path to deploying such displays in the future, using current Sensor-in-Pixel (SIP)
LCD panels, which physically collocate sensing and display elements.},
