Unistroke style, and affixed with a straight tail. We designed a tentative touch device
interaction technique that supports fast interactions with large sets of commands,
is easily discoverable, improves user's recall at no speed cost, and supports fluid
transition from novice to expert mode. An experiment suggests that Augmented Letters
outperform Marking Menu in terms of user recall.},
